                <ul>
                    <li>All-new Preview Mode that shows your file</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.9" date="2017-09-17">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Resourceful Little Worker</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fix the bug that recreates old files when not needed</li>
                    <li>New icon that matches the brand of Quilter more</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.8" date="2017-09-06">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Colors are Nice</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Use colors that make sense for the app</li>
                    <li>Make the toolbar stand out less for focus</li>
                    <li>Minor fixes in the headerbar subtitle for files</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.7" date="2017-09-03">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Open the Box</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fix opening a file from outside the app</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.6" date="2017-09-03">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Save Button &amp; One Window</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Add a toggle for the save button on new openings of the app</li>
                    <li>Make Quilter behave like a One-Window App to disallow rogue instances</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.5" date="2017-08-06">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Unnecessary Saving Dialogs</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Remove an unnecessary save dialog when opening new files</li>
                    <li>Fix autosaving</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.4" date="2017-08-06">
            <description>
                <p>Release: New Colors &amp; Layout</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>A new and fresh coat of paint following the elementary Palette</li>
                    <li>Centered the layout of the text view for the Edit View</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.3" date="2017-08-02">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Files &amp; Subtitles</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>File I/O now works properly</li>
                    <li>Organized code properly now</li>
                    <li>New font for better reading</li>
                    <li>Fixed the subtitle showing the current file</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.2" date="2017-07-28">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Shortcuts to Time &amp; Space</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Actually open/save documents when using the Ctrl-S/Ctrl-O shortcuts</li>
                    <li>Remove the About Dialog</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.1" date="2017-07-25">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Highlight What's Important</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed the selection bug when using the Quilter style schemes outside Quilter</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
        <release version="1.2.0" date="2017-07-10">
            <description>
                <p>Release: Timebomb No More, Darling!</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed the "timed crash" on saving the file</li>
                    <li>Save window width &amp; height on close</li>
                </ul>
            </description>
        </release>
